* MOSFET CS amplifier
VDD vdd 0 DC 12.45
Vin in 0 AC 1
Cin in gate 22u
RG1 vdd gate 1.2Meg
RG2 gate 0 680k
RD vdd drain 15k
M1 drain gate source 0 NMOS1
RS source 0 8.2k
Cout drain out 6.8u
Rload out 0 150k
.model NMOS1 NMOS (Level=1 VTO=2.0 KP=1.0e-3 L=2e-6 W=50e-6 Lambda=0.0 Gamma=0.0 Phi=0.6)
.ac dec 50 10 10Meg
.print ac V(out)
.end